task.summary: -added support for filtering presets so user doesn't have to enter rows/keys for frequently used data files. -finished filterByKey logic. -started some unit tests.
-added example input files to resources -worked on FilterPresetsSpec

-fixed bug where delimiter for presets wasn't being passed properly to filterResultsHandler -removed some redundant traits -updated pattern matching for presets in Parsomatic -converted ParsomaticParser to use recursive function instead of while loop. -Streamlined presets.
-fixed bug where delimiter for presets wasn't being passed properly to filterResultsHandler -removed some redundant traits -updated pattern matching for presets in Parsomatic
-completed unit tests for input processor and map to objects
-made change so empty lines don't get into ListBuffer generated from file. This required changes to presets.
-completed GetPicardMeanQualMetrics & associated unit test -created associated case for pattern matching in MapToObject -completed preset for GetPicardMeanQualMetrics
-Added presets and associated processing code for ERCC stats, Mean GC, Mean Qual.
-added sampleId to command-line arguments and config.

-implemented reflection in ObjectToMd in order to be able to handle each metric type without having to do pattern matching. -refactored MapToAnalysisObject to return an Analysis Object instead of a metrics list. -added OnComplete handling at top level of application so as to gracefully exit program after post request to DB is made.
-updated to include argument for sample ID and sample ref ID
